@@ -0,0 +1,54 @@
+# Rigging
+
+Project tooling values for Shipshape roles. Values only, not procedure.
+Procedure lives in the skills. Every role reads this on open.
+
+## Stack
+
+- language: JavaScript
+- runtime: Node.js
+- packageManager: npm
+
+## Directories
+
+- implementation: src/
+- specs: features/
+- verification: features/support/
+- assets: data/
+- scantlings: none
+
+## Commands
+
+- discover: `npx cucumber-js --dry-run`
+- focused: `npx cucumber-js --name "{scenario}"`
+- broad: `npx cucumber-js --tags "not @captain and not @shipwright" --format progress`
+- coverage: none
+- step-usage: `npx cucumber-js --format usage`
+- plank-inventory: `grep -r "@planks" src/ features/support/ 2>/dev/null`
+- typecheck: `node --check src/tide.js`
+- lint: `npx biome check src/ features/`
+- conformance: none
+
+## Perturbation
+
+- message: `PERTURBATION: consider current durable context; remove when fixed`
+- perturb: `throw new Error("PERTURBATION: consider current durable context; remove when fixed");`
+
+## Tiers
+
+- default: @logic
+- sandbox: none
+- policy: default credential source is none
+- weather: none
+- runrecord: none
+
+## Dependencies
+
+- policy: none
+- dependency: none
+
+## Outbound
+
+- outbound: none
+- ship: none
+- verify: none
