new file mode 100644
index 0000000..3948012
--- /dev/null
+++ b/features/data-catalog.feature
@@ -0,0 +1,12 @@
+Feature: Data catalog integrity
+
+  Scenario: Stations data is referenced by step definitions
+    Given the data catalog at data/stations.json
+    When the step-definition coverage is analysed
+    Then the stations catalog is referenced by at least one step definition
+
+  @captain
+  Scenario: Step definitions use configured data paths
+    Given the step definitions in features/support/
+    When the data-path references are inspected
+    Then all data file references use an asset path from the assets directory
